{"id": "1366801843455393844", "channel_id": "1366327293873488025", "type": 0, "author_id": "157679037240573953", "author_name": "monchi3524", "author_bot": false, "content": "Absolutely agree with this suggestion: If a player receives either an Awaker or Wheel of Destiny within the first 90 rolls, the following 90 rolls should guarantee the other item they have not yet obtained.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T15:42:33.430000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366327293873488025", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[Suggesion] [Feedback] About Unfair Self-Select Awakening Event", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1366816893339697193", "channel_id": "1366327293873488025", "type": 0, "author_id": "328412633176866827", "author_name": "glacy_9918", "author_bot": false, "content": "I think a better way is just simply have two separate pools, one for awakers and one for wheels, just like the original one. I don't see any reason to have such a special design<:processing:1357185814567718963>", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T16:42:21.602000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366327293873488025", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[Suggesion] [Feedback] About Unfair Self-Select Awakening Event", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1366818699134242887", "channel_id": "1366327293873488025", "type": 0, "author_id": "1323593366017146992", "author_name": "nowimfaceless", "author_bot": false, "content": "如下是本篇文章内容的中文翻译，便于使用中文的玩家理解：\n\n忘却前夜的开发者们你们好：\n我是“忘却前夜泰国频道”的管理员，今日，我收到了来自泰国玩家的大量有关于「久远的呼唤」自选唤醒活动公平性的反馈。\n将唤醒体和命轮合并于一个up池中的行为被认为是极为不恰当的，尤其是对于那些非开服玩家。\n例如，有些玩家为了获取某位唤醒体而投入了全部的资源但是只获取了未up角色（简而言之，歪了）。\n真正的问题在于，玩家在唤醒过程中连续获得两张甚至三张命轮，但没有一个唤醒体。这让很多新玩家感到沮丧，以至于他们表达出了退坑的想法。\n以下是我想提出的一些反馈和建议：\n-像往常的up池一样，分开up唤醒体和命轮；\n或\n-如果玩家在前90抽中获得了唤醒体或命轮，那么接下来的90抽内应该保证他们能获得剩下的那个还没有获得的东西。在两者均被获得后，从第270抽开始系统可以随机分配获得的是唤醒体还是命轮。\n我真诚地希望你们的团队能考虑我们的反馈，这是首个我感受到对0氪和氪金玩家都公平而尊重对待的游戏（译者注：译者本人对这句话持有保留意见）。\n我真的希望忘却前夜可以保持其优势……就像我初见它时那样。\n最好的问候", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T16:49:32.137000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366327293873488025", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[Suggesion] [Feedback] About Unfair Self-Select Awakening Event", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
